above mentioned project homepage you can find all license conditions
of the incorporated software products in OpenCCU.</p>
<p>In case of problems/suggestions or feature requests please use the
<a href=https://homematic-forum.de/forum/viewforum.php?f=65>OpenCCU discussion platform</a>
or in case of reproducible issues please use the issue-tracker on the
project homepage itself.</p>
<p>If you want to support the development of OpenCCU by contributing
your own software skills or want to contribute in other way (e.g.
writing documentation, etc.) please visit our <a href=https://github.com/OpenCCU/OpenCCU>project homepage</a>
for more information how to contribute.
